<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2>Learn Azure AD & Azure AD B2C</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Welcome to the hand-on labs on Azure AD & Azure AD B2C. Here you will find information required for your day. This web site has several helper sections and several "challenge verification" sections. You fill find a lot of useful resource on this home page.
        </p>
