<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Step 1 - Deploy App</h3>
        <p>Congratulations, if you are seeing this page, you have already successfully deployed your demo application. All challenges will be completed using your application and your B2C tenant.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Step 2 - Configure App</h3>
        <p>When you are ready with your Azure AD SSO for SaaS Apps you may proceed to <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="RequiredSetup">Required Setup</a> and setup your site for Azure AD B2C Challenges</p>
        <p><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="RequiredSetup" class="btn btn-primary">Required Setup &rarr;</a></p>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Step 3 - Proceed to Challenges</h3>
        <p>Once you setup your website with your Azure AD B2C Tenant you can proceed to the <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Challenges">Challenges</a>.</p>
        <p><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Challenges" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Challenges &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>

